Cell["\<\
Stuff to add:
1. Decomposition of basis(theta) in terms of tetrad vectors - DONE
2. Check orthogonality properties of basis tensors
3. Perturbative expansion of basis coefficients when looking at perturbations \
of polarization tensor\
\>", "Text",
